+/**
+ * An implementation of {@link AwsCredentialsProvider} that is extended within this package to provide support for periodically
+ * updating session credentials. The credential provider loads configuration from a {@link ProfileFile}, and use this information
+ * to generate a cached token directory. With this directory the information a {@link SsoClient} can do a
+ * {@link SsoClient#getRoleCredentials(Consumer)} call to retrieve the credentials needed.
+ *
+ * When credentials get close to expiration, this class will attempt to update them asynchronously using
+ * {@link SsoCredentialsUtils#getUpdatedCredentials()}. If the credentials end up expiring, this class will block all calls
+ * to {@link #resolveCredentials()} until the credentials can be updated.
+ */
